{"type":null,"faqId":43865,"title":"如何使用B2找手机","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">前提：手环和手机蓝牙连接成功且华为穿戴APP在后台运行，才可以通过手环寻找手机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 长按手环侧按键3s进入菜单界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 下滑B2屏幕进入找手机界面：</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=154726\" style=\"width:0.30763888in;height:0.43541667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=154727\" style=\"width:0.3125in;height:0.4375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=154728\" style=\"width:0.30833334in;height:0.43611112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 点击找手机图标。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 手机发出林志玲女神“我在这里，我在这里”的音乐，找到手机。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9366","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399712000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":20,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"B,找手机,使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}